title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Auto Shop Robbery Contracts
content:
After getting your hands dirty tuning up rides for gearheads across the city, swing by the Job Board in your Auto Shop to browse available Robbery Contracts — paying out 2X GTA$ and RP all week long.

It’s a good time to get into the custom vehicles business with Auto Shop properties and their Upgrades and Modifications discounted at 30% off through November 27.
